## ğŸ§© Modules

Inside the example folder youâ€™ll also find an [example module](examples/example_module) to get you started.
Use it as an inspiration for your own modules or generate basic modules using the Flask++ CLI. ğŸ˜‰

`fpp modules create module_name`

